This is the README file for IOI 2001 competition task Score.

This directory includes
- the task description, score.rtf
- competition files to describe the "board", ie the position and
  arrow information, score_n.in, where n=1,..,20
- code for the optimal player/opponent, score.cpp

If you want to know why the optimal player is optimal, 
please see the IOI 2001 publication, which you can ftp from
ftp://ftp.cs.uta.fi/pub/reports/pdf/A-2001-7.pdf



